      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p161_s0021",
      "text": "When N_Port Login is ended with a Fabric present, the value of end-to-end Credit is initialized.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        250.97,
        539.99,
        262.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p161_s0022",
      "text": "When N_Port Login is ended in a point-to-point topology, the values of buffer-to-buffer and end-to-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        262.97,
        540.03,
        274.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p161_s0023",
