      "text": "b) in Class 2, the Responder has received the ACK (EOF",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        370.97,
        363.47,
        382.08
      ],
      "block_index": 14,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p161_s0033",
