        452.86,
        382.08
      ],
      "block_index": 14,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 3
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p161_s0035",
      "text": "c)",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        394.97,
        114.38,
        406.08
      ],
      "block_index": 15,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p161_s0036",
      "text": "in Class 3, the Responder has transmitted the LS_ACC.",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        394.97,
        369.58,
        406.08
      ],
      "block_index": 15,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p161_s0037",
      "text": "When N_Port Login is ended with a Fabric present, the value of end-to-end Credit is initialized.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        418.97,
        540.0,
        430.08
      ],
      "block_index": 16,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p161_s0038",
      "text": "When N_Port Login is ended in a point-to-point topology, the values of buffer-to-buffer and end-to-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        430.97,
        540.03,
        442.08
      ],
      "block_index": 16,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p161_s0039",
      "text": "end Credit are initialized.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        442.97,
        206.02,
        454.08
      ],
      "block_index": 16,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p161_s0040",
      "text": "6.4",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        466.96,
        109.88,
        478.08
      ],
      "block_index": 17,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p161_s0041",
      "text": "Logout",
      "bbox": [
        119.88,
        466.96,
        153.74,
        478.08
      ],
      "block_index": 17,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p161_s0042",
      "text": "6.4.1",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        490.96,
        118.22,
        502.08
      ],
      "block_index": 18,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p161_s0043",
      "text": "Introduction",
      "bbox": [
        128.22,
        490.96,
        186.53,
        502.08
      ],
      "block_index": 18,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p161_s0044",
      "text": "The destination Logout procedure provides a method for removing service between two N_Port_IDs",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        514.96,
        540.13,
        526.08
      ],
      "block_index": 19,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p161_s0045",
      "text": "or between an N_Port_ID and a Fabric. Logout releases resources, identifiers, and relationships as-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        526.96,
        540.04,
        538.08
      ],
      "block_index": 19,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p161_s0046",
      "text": "sociated with maintaining service between an N_Port_ID and a destination N_Port_ID or Fabric. Ex-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        538.96,
        540.01,
        550.08
      ],
      "block_index": 19,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p161_s0047",
      "text": "plicit Nx_Port Logout may be requested by an Nx_Port to another Nx_Port (see 6.4.2). Explicit Fabric",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        550.96,
        540.04,
        562.08
      ],
      "block_index": 19,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p161_s0048",
      "text": "Logout may be requested by an Nx_Port to a Fabric (e.g., to remove a virtual N_Port_ID previously",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        562.96,
        539.97,
        574.08
      ],
      "block_index": 19,
      "line_index": 5,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p161_s0049",
      "text": "assigned by the Fabric) or by a Fabric to an Nx_Port (see 6.4.3). Implicit Logout may occur between",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        574.96,
        540.0,
        586.08
      ],
      "block_index": 19,
      "line_index": 6,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p161_s0050",
      "text": "an Nx_Port and the Fabric (see 6.4.4).",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        586.96,
        265.97,
        598.08
      ],
      "block_index": 19,
      "line_index": 7,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p161_s0051",
      "text": "6.4.2",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        610.96,
        118.22,
        622.08
      ],
      "block_index": 20,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p161_s0052",
      "text": "Explicit N_Port Logout",
      "bbox": [
        128.22,
        610.96,
        235.95,
        622.08
      ],
      "block_index": 20,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p161_s0053",
      "text": "Logout is accomplished by transmitting a Logout (LOGO) Link Service request Sequence (see FC-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        635.02,
        540.06,
        646.14
      ],
      "block_index": 21,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p161_s0054",
      "text": "FS-2) to a destination Nx_Port.  The Logout procedure is complete when the responding Nx_Port",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        647.02,
        540.03,
        658.14
      ],
      "block_index": 21,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p161_s0055",
      "text": "transmits a LS_ACC Link Service reply Sequence.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        659.02,
        318.69,
        670.14
      ],
      "block_index": 21,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p161_s0056",
      "text": "To explicitly Logout, the initiating Nx_Port shall terminate other open Sequences that it initiated with",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        683.02,
        540.02,
        694.14
      ],
      "block_index": 22,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p161_s0057",
      "text": "the destination Nx_Port prior to performing Logout, otherwise, the state of other open Sequences is",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        695.02,
        540.01,
        706.14
      ],
      "block_index": 22,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    }
  ],
  "asset_ids": []
}